BUSHE KUTI MWATILA Satana . . .
Bubifi ububa mu muntu
Satana alilanshenyepo na Yesu kabili ‘ alimutunkilepo ’ .
Ilyo Lesa amubumbile , Satana ali ni malaika umusuma , lelo “ tatwalilile mu cine . ”
Aishileba uwa bufi kabili alipondokeele Lesa .
Bamalaika bambi nabo balipondokeele Lesa nga filya Satana acitile . — Ukusokolola 12 : 9 .
Satana alapofwisha abantu abengi ukufika fye na lelo . — 2 Abena Korinti 4 : 4 .
ABANTU BAMO BATILA Satana Kaseebanya te utunka abantu , e lyo bambi nabo balatiina sana imipashi yabipa .
Satana alikwata sana amaka ya kutungulula abantu , na lyo line , te bantu bonse atungulula .
Satana alaifungushanya pa kuti alelufya abantu abengi . — 2 Abena Korinti 11 : 14 .
Inshita shimo imipashi yabipa ilatungulula abantu . — Mateo 12 : 22 .
Lesa kuti amwafwa “ ukukaana Satana Kaseebanya . ” — Yakobo 4 : 7 .
1 : 16 .
Ni nshila nshi iikalamba iyo Yehova alangilamo icikuuku ku bantunse ?
Kuti twalanga shani ukuti nomba tatutungululwa no lubembu lelo tutungululwa ne cikuuku ca kwa Lesa ?
Mapaalo nshi tukwata pa mulandu wa cikuuku ca kwa Yehova ?
1 , 2 . ( a ) Londololeni icilangililo Yesu alandile ica mwine we bala lya myangashi . ( b ) Bushe ili lyashi lilanga shani ukuti Lesa ni kapekape kabili wa cikuuku ?
Bushe ico mwabela ne linso ilibi ni co ndi muntu umusuma ? ’ — Mat .
( Belengeni 2 Abena Korinti 6 : 1 . )
Bushe Yehova acitile shani pa kulanga ukuti wa cikuuku ku bantunse bonse , kabili mulandu nshi acitile ifi ?
Ni mwi mwalola amashiwi ya kuti Yehova alanga icikuuku cakwe mu “ nshila ishalekanalekana ” ?
Umutumwa Petro atile : “ Imwe bonse Lesa alimupeela ubupe bwaibela umo umo . Apo muli babomfi abasuma abo Lesa alanga icikuuku mu nshila shalekanalekana , mulebomfya ubupe Lesa amupeela ku kubombela abanenu . ”
Umutumwa Yohane alembele ukuti : “ Bonse twapokelele sana icikuuku ca kwa Lesa kuli ena , pantu alifulisha icikuuku ca kwa Lesa . ”
Bushe tunonkelamo shani mu cikuuku ca kwa Yehova , kabili finshi tulingile ukulacita pa kulanga ukuti tulatasha pa cikuuku cakwe ?
( Belengeni 1 Yohane 1 : 8 , 9 . )
Finshi tuipakisha pa mulandu wa cikuuku ca kwa Lesa ?
Inshila isho Lesa atulangilamo icikuuku : Ishuko lya kumfwa imbila nsuma ( Moneni paragrafu 11 )
Bushe abasubwa balenga shani aba mu “ mpaanga shimbi ” ukuba abalungami ?
Ishuko lya kulanda na Lesa mwi pepo ( Moneni paragrafu 12 )
Bushe ipepo lyayampana shani ne cikuuku ca kwa Lesa ?
Bushe Lesa mu cikuuku cakwe atwafwa shani “ pa nshita tulekabila ubwafwilisho ” ?
Bushe tunonkelamo shani mu icikuuku ca kwa Yehova ?
Lisubilo nshi twakwata pa mulandu wa cikuuku ca kwa Lesa ?
( Belengeni Amalumbo 49 : 7 , 8 . )
Bushe Abena Kristu bamo aba mu nshiku sha batumwa balemona shani icikuuku ca kwa Lesa ?
Milimo nshi twakwata pa mulandu wa cikuuku ca kwa Yehova ?
Mulimo nshi twakwata uo tukalandapo mu cipande cikonkelepo ?
Mu cipande cikonkelepo tukalanda pali uyu umulimo .
20 : 24 .
Finshi icikuuku ca kwa Lesa cilingile ukutucincisha ukulacita ?
Bushe “ imbila nsuma iya Bufumu ” ilanga shani icikuuku ca kwa Lesa ?
Bushe Yehova akalanga shani icikuuku cakwe mu calo cipya ?
Bushe umutumwa Paulo alangile shani ukuti aletasha pa cikuuku ca kwa Lesa ?
UMUTUMWA Paulo alilandile ukwabula ukupita na mu mbali ukuti : “ Icikuuku cakwe [ Lesa ] ico nalangilwe tacali ica fye . ”
( Belengeni 1 Abena Korinti 15 : 9 , 10 . )
( Belengeni Abena Efese 3 : 5 - 8 . )
Cinshi twingalandila ukuti tapaba ubupusano pa “ mbila nsuma iya Bufumu ” e lyo ne mbila nsuma iya “ cikuuku ca kwa Lesa ” ?
Bushe ukusambilisha abantu pa cilubula kwayampana shani no kubila imbila nsuma ya cikuuku ca kwa Lesa ?
Mulandu nshi abantunse ababembu balingile ukubwelela kuli Lesa ?
Umutumwa Yohane alembele ukuti : “ Uutetekela Umwana aba no mweo wa muyayaya ; uushumfwila Mwana takabe no mweo , lelo ubukali bwa kwa Lesa bwaikala pali ena . ”
9 , 10 . ( a ) Mulimo nshi Kristu apeele abasubwa ?
E ico ifwe tuli nkombe ishibomba umulimo wa kwa Kristu , caba kwati ni fwe Lesa alebomfya ukukunkumba abantu .
Mulandu nshi ukwafwa abantu ukwishiba ukutila kuti bapepa kuli Yehova kwabela ni mbila nsuma ?
Abantu abengi balapepa pa kuti fye bomfweko bwino , lelo bamona kwati Lesa tomfwa amapepo yabo .
Balingile baishiba ukuti Yehova ‘ alomfwa ipepo . ’
Uwaimbile amalumbo Davidi aimbile ati : “ Mwe bomfwa ipepo , kuli imwe e ko abantunse bakesa .
Yesu afundile abasambi bakwe ati : “ Nga mwalombela icintu conse mwi shina lyandi , nkacicita . ”
13 , 14 . ( a ) Lishuko nshi abasubwa bakakwata ku ntanshi ?
( b ) Finshi abasubwa bakacitila abantunse ?
Bushe Yehova akalanga shani icikuuku cakwe ku ba mu “ mpaanga shimbi ” ku ntanshi ?
Abantu abengi nga nshi abafwa ukwabula ukwishiba Lesa nabo bene bakabuushiwa .
Yohane alembele ati : “ Namwene abafwa , bashimucindikwa na bantu yaweyawe , nabeminina ku cinso ca cipuna ca bufumu , na mabuuku yapombwa yalifungulwilwe .
Na bafwa babapingwilile ku fyalembelwe mwi buuku ukulingana ne fyo balecita .
Bemba alekele abafwa abalimo , ne mfwa ne Nshiishi na fyo fyalekele abafwa abalimo , kabili bonse bapingwilwe ukulingana ne fyo balecita . ”
Cinshi tulingile ukulatontonkanyapo ilyo tulebomba umulimo wa kubila ?
Baibolo itila : “ Ifibumbwa na fyo fikalubuka ku busha bwa kubola no kuba abana ba kwa Lesa . ”
Kabili , atile : “ Lemba , pantu aya mashiwi ya cishinka kabili ya cine . ”
Nga tulebila sana imbila nsuma ninshi tulelumbanya Yehova pa cikuuku cakwe !
“ Mulefwaya ubufumu bwakwe [ Lesa ] , na fyonse ifi akamupeela . ” — LUKA 12 : 31 .
Bupusano nshi bwaba pa fyo tukabila na pa fyo tufwaya ?
Mulandu nshi tushilingile ukulafwaila ukukwata ifintu ifingi ?
Cinshi calenga mushininkishe ukuti Yehova kuti amupeela ifyo mukabila cila bushiku ?
Bushe Satana abomfya shani “ ulunkumbwa lwa menso ” ?
Muleibukisha ifyo umutumwa Yohane atusokele ati : “ Icalo cileya pamo no lunkumbwa lwa ciko . ”
Cinshi cingacitikila ababika fye amano ku kufwaya ifyuma ?
Finshi twalalandapo , kabili mulandu nshi ?
8 , 9 . ( a ) Cinshi ico tushilingile ukusakamanina sana pa fyo tukabila ?
( b ) Finshi Yesu aishibe pa bantu na pa fyo bakabila ?
Ilyo Yesu asambilishe abasambi bakwe ifya kupepa , cinshi alandile ukuti e co balingile ukubikako sana amano ?
Finshi tulesambilila ku fyo Yehova asakamana ifyuni fya mu muulu ?
Tulingile ‘ ukulolekesha ifyuni fya mu muulu . ’
Kwena Yehova tabika ifya kulya mu tunwa twa fyuni !
Cinshi cilanga ukuti twalicindama ukucila ifyuni fya mu muulu ?
( Linganyeniko Luka 12 : 6 , 7 . )
15 , 16 . ( a ) Finshi twingasambilila ku fyo Yehova asakamana amaluba ya mu mpanga ?
( Moneni icikope pa ntendekelo ya cino cipande . ) ( b ) Cipusho nshi nalimo twingayipusha , kabili mulandu nshi ?
Finshi Yehova aishiba pali ifwe umo umo , kabili finshi akatucitila ?
Mulandu nshi tushilingile ukusakamanina pa fingacitika ku ntanshi ?
